title: HOUR 1 - Russell Wilson, NFL Injuries
itunes:title: HOUR 1 - Russell Wilson, NFL Injuries
description:
Brian Noe, Rich Ohrnberger, and Geoff Schwartz react to Russell Wilson getting a huge extension with the Denver Broncos. The guys examine what an expanded College Football Playoff field could do for the sport. Plus, what team has taken the biggest loss on their offensive line over preseason?
